"    </p>",
"    <p>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/13/1236?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD), including emphysema (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/25/29075?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Asthma inhaler techniques in adults (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?19/13/19670?source=see_link\">",
